title: Photos: Baylor shows up in grey, makes Tech pay in AT&T Stadium rout
text: Baylor Bears running back Shock Linwood (32) scores a rushing touchdown in the first quarter to make the score 6-0 during an NCAA football game between Texas Tech and Baylor at AT&T Stadium in Arlington, Texas Saturday October 3, 2015. (Andy Jacobsohn/The Dallas Morning News)
